name: The Polish Ambassador to Space 'Golden Moments'

metadata.name: Polish2Space Golden Moments #1
metadata.description: The Polish Ambassador (electronic music composer) reveals his genesis NFT drop! A 567 collection of his favorite frames from The Polish Ambassador to Space graphic novel released in 2021. Grab a copy of the graphic novel, listen to the soundtrack and now own a piece of the web3 expansion of this amazing multimedia project!
